headline: SKYBOXE Secures Nationwide Network Certification from T-Mobile for its 5G Fixed Wireless Access Router
summary: SKYBOXE®, the new 5G company that's on a mission to "unwire" American households, today announced that its flagship 5G Fixed Wireless Access (FWA) Router has officially received certification from T-Mobile. This milestone is mission-critical for SKYBOXE, as it expands compatibility across T-Mobile's nationwide 5G footprint.
